</style>
<!-- END APPRAISAL FORM -->
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      I understand the buyer who is choosing Banyo today. It is overwhelmingly a buyer making a deliberate trade: more land, a train station and a quieter street, in exchange for moving one suburb further out from Nundah or Northgate. Reading where a Banyo property sits on that trade is the difference between a quick competitive campaign and a long sit on market.
    </p>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      Banyo train station on the Shorncliffe line puts the CBD inside 20 minutes by rail, and the Gateway Motorway interchange a few minutes north gives drivers fast access to the airport, the eastern suburbs and the Sunshine Coast. The Australian Catholic University Banyo campus on Nudgee Road creates a base of staff and student rental demand that supports the suburb's investor segment, while St Pius X Parish and Mary MacKillop College anchor family buyer interest around the eastern and southern pockets of the suburb. Banyo Village on St Vincents Road has been progressively revitalised with cafes, a Coles supermarket and a wine bar precinct, which has materially shifted the suburb's day-to-day amenity and brought it into walkable-village territory. The elevated streets to the east of the rail line carry a clear premium over the flatter western sections.
    </p>
    <div style="display:flex; gap:1.5rem; flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <div style="flex:1; min-width:200px; background:#fff; padding:1.75rem; border-left:3px solid #c4912a;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:400; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Inner North Specialist</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560;">Shorncliffe line train suburb</p>
      </div>
      <div style="flex:1; min-width:200px; background:#fff; padding:1.75rem; border-left:3px solid #c4912a;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:400; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Gentrification Market</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560;">Banyo Village revival</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p style="font-size:0.82rem;color:#78716c;margin-top:2rem;">Also selling in: <a href="/suburbs/nudgee" style="color:#c4912a;">Nudgee</a>, <a href="/suburbs/northgate" style="color:#c4912a;">Northgate</a>, <a href="/suburbs/nundah" style="color:#c4912a;">Nundah</a>.</p>
  </div>
</section>

